room_title: Escape room "Zombie Apocalypse" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: We went for a 14-year-old birthday party to the zombie room. The turned the scare down so the younger members of the party weren't too scared. All of the kids (husband included) want to do it again. The staff was exceptional!

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Apocalypse" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: We had a great time fun friendly people. Challenging to get the clues gathered without the zombie getting us. We solved it just a couple minutes left Would highly recommended.

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Apocalypse" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: We came as a work group today and did the Zombie Apocalypse room. It was a great team building exercise. I would recommend this to any group for a great time.

room_title: Escape room "Zombie Apocalypse" by House of Conundrum in Omaha
review: The girls and I had a great time! We did the Zombie Apocalypse room and it was awesome! Highly recommend going!
